<plot>The outcome of experimental battlefield surgery is something more than human. A unique weapons-grade warrior, Nathan Frost now has abilities that far surpass human physical limits. Now, Frost is the best chance against the world's next Terrorist Sovereign. In a last attempt to restore Peace, War shall rage. Experience the dramatic intensity of the frontlines of a war through the eyes of the first of a new breed of super soldiers in this gritty and epic first-person action game. Eleven missions spanning across 16 maps including the Opera House turned Prison, a Buddhist Temple converted to a Military Base, and the sprawling urban Wastelands.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?446044</url></doc>
